high_descs: turn around, and cross the room to the sink. turn to face the sink
take the spoon on the sink divider
shift slightly right, to stop in front of and facing the right-hand sink
place the spoon in the sink, rinse it, and then remove the spoon from the sink
open the drawer, place the spoon in the front of the drawer, and close the drawer
anns.task_desc: place a rinsed spoon into the drawer

high_descs: Turn and cross the kitchen to the sink, which will be on your right.
Pick up the spoon from the drying rack on the left side of the sink.
Move a step to the right and place the spoon in the right side of the sink.
Turn on the water and remove the spoon after it has been washed.
Turn to your left, so you're facing the dishwasher while still standing at the sink.
Open the top drawer on your right that's closest to the corner of the counter and place the spoon  inside.
anns.task_desc: Put a washed spoon in a drawer.

high_descs: Turn around, go straight towards the dishwasher, turn right, go to the sink.
Take the spoon from the sink's drying rack.
Go right slightly while facing towards the sink.
Wash the spoon in the sink. Take the spoon from the sink.
Put the spoon in the drawer on the right closes to the corner under the counter.
anns.task_desc: Put a spoon in a drawer.
